title: Spittin’ Chiclets Episode 401: Featuring Scott Parker
description:
On this week’s episode of Spittin’ Chiclets, the guys are joined by Scott Parker (01:01). Scott joined us live in Denver to discuss his career, his time with the Avs, and some hilarious stories along the way.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
